  <entry>
    <title>我的博客搭建过程</title>
    <link href="http://yoursite.com/2019/12/02/%E6%88%91%E7%9A%84%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E8%BF%87%E7%A8%8B/"/>
    <id>http://yoursite.com/2019/12/02/%E6%88%91%E7%9A%84%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E8%BF%87%E7%A8%8B/</id>
    <published>2019-12-02T02:53:40.000Z</published>
    <updated>2019-12-02T02:54:38.843Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="准备条件"><a href="#准备条件" class="headerlink" title="准备条件"></a>准备条件</h1><ul><li>GitHub提供了 <strong>GitHub Pages</strong> ：帮助架设一个静态网站 （解决没有服务器的问题）</li><li>Hexo博客框架：轻量级、MarkDown直接写文章、直接将文章编译成静态网页文件并发布（文章相关信息不必存储在数据库中了，属于纯静态页面，解决没有数据库的问题）</li><li>GitHub Pages允许每个账户创建一个名为{username}.github.io的仓库、并自动为这个仓库分配一个github.io的二级域名（解决了没有域名的问题）、也可以支持自定义域名</li></ul><h1 id="新建项目"><a href="#新建项目" class="headerlink" title="新建项目"></a>新建项目</h1><ul><li><p>在GitHub新建一个仓库，名称为{username}.github.io</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">必须以.github.io为后缀结尾</span></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="C:%5CUsers%5Cpc%5CAppData%5CRoaming%5CTypora%5Ctypora-user-images%5Cimage-20191201223952061.png" alt="image-20191201223952061"></p></li><li><p>为了和后面的配置相呼应，应该去配置GitHub的SSH链接</p></li></ul><h1 id="安装环境"><a href="#安装环境" class="headerlink" title="安装环境"></a>安装环境</h1><ul><li>Node.js</li><li>Hexo</li></ul><h1 id="初始化项目"><a href="#初始化项目" class="headerlink" title="初始化项目"></a>初始化项目</h1><ul><li><p>使用Hexo的命令行创建一个项目</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo init [name]</span></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>[name] 即项目名，我这里写<code>chenyuanyuyang</code>。</p><p><img src="C:%5CUsers%5Cpc%5CAppData%5CRoaming%5CTypora%5Ctypora-user-images%5Cimage-20191201230119338.png" alt="image-20191201230119338"></p><p>可以看到这里生成的文件：</p><p><img src="C:%5CUsers%5Cpc%5CAppData%5CRoaming%5CTypora%5Ctypora-user-images%5Cimage-20191201230247151.png" alt="image-20191201230247151"></p></li><li><p>进入新生成的文件夹里，将Hexo编译生成HTML代码：</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo generate</span></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="C:%5CUsers%5Cpc%5CAppData%5CRoaming%5CTypora%5Ctypora-user-images%5Cimage-20191201230153889.png" alt="image-20191201230153889"></p><p> 新生成的包含了js、css、source等文件夹，都包含在了public里面：</p><p><img src="C:%5CUsers%5Cpc%5CAppData%5CRoaming%5CTypora%5Ctypora-user-images%5Cimage-20191201230457296.png" alt="image-20191201230457296"></p></li><li><p>将博客在本地运行：</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo serve</span></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="C:%5CUsers%5Cpc%5CAppData%5CRoaming%5CTypora%5Ctypora-user-images%5Cimage-20191201230551648.png" alt="image-20191201230551648"></p><p>它告诉我们可以在本地通过4000端口访问：</p><p><img src="C:%5CUsers%5Cpc%5CAppData%5CRoaming%5CTypora%5Ctypora-user-images%5Cimage-20191201230659913.png" alt="image-20191201230659913"></p></li></ul><h1 id="部署"><a href="#部署" class="headerlink" title="部署"></a>部署</h1><p>接下来进行部署，把这个初始化的博客放到GitHub Pages上验证它的可用性。验证可用后再进行后续的修改。</p><ul><li><p>配置部署信息：修改根目录下的_config.yml文件</p><p><img src="C:%5CUsers%5Cpc%5CAppData%5CRoaming%5CTypora%5Ctypora-user-images%5Cimage-20191201231144472.png" alt="image-20191201231144472"></p></li><li><p>安装支持Git的部署插件，名字叫做hexo-deployer-git。在项目目录下执行：</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install hexo-deployer-git --save</span></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="C:%5CUsers%5Cpc%5CAppData%5CRoaming%5CTypora%5Ctypora-user-images%5Cimage-20191201231455418.png" alt="image-20191201231455418"></p></li><li><p>利用Hexo一键部署：</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo deploy</span></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>期间会要求输入SSH密码：</p><p><img src="C:%5CUsers%5Cpc%5CAppData%5CRoaming%5CTypora%5Ctypora-user-images%5Cimage-20191202002553614.png" alt="image-20191202002553614"></p><p>部署成功。出现下面的信息就证明博客已经被部署到GitHub Pages页面上了。这时我们访问这个仓库的同名链接，比如我的是：<a href="http://chenyuanyuyang.github.io" target="_blank" rel="noopener">http://chenyuanyuyang.github.io</a></p><p><img src="C:%5CUsers%5Cpc%5CAppData%5CRoaming%5CTypora%5Ctypora-user-images%5Cimage-20191202002631165.png" alt="image-20191202002631165"></p><p>同时可以去查看我们的GitHub仓库：里面实际是博客文件夹下面的public文件夹下的所有内容。Hexo把编译之后的静态页面内容都上传到GitHub的master分支上去了。</p><p><img src="C:%5CUsers%5Cpc%5CAppData%5CRoaming%5CTypora%5Ctypora-user-images%5Cimage-20191202003035536.png" alt="image-20191202003035536"></p></li></ul><h1 id="配置站点信息"><a href="#配置站点信息" class="headerlink" title="配置站点信息"></a>配置站点信息</h1><ul><li><p>修改根目录下的_config.yml文件。根据需要自定义。</p><p><img src="C:%5CUsers%5Cpc%5CAppData%5CRoaming%5CTypora%5Ctypora-user-images%5Cimage-20191202003802195.png" alt="image-20191202003802195"></p></li></ul><h1 id="主题配置"><a href="#主题配置" class="headerlink" title="主题配置"></a>主题配置</h1><p>这里推荐的是Hexo里面应用最多的主题：Next。它支持插件功能极为丰富。</p><p>可以直接到Next主题的<a href="https://github.com/theme-next/hexo-theme-next" target="_blank" rel="noopener">GitHub Repository</a>下载</p><ul><li><p>下载。成功后Next主题的源码会出现在/themes/next文件夹下</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git clone https:&#x2F;&#x2F;github.com&#x2F;theme-next&#x2F;hexo-theme-next themes&#x2F;next</span></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="C:%5CUsers%5Cpc%5CAppData%5CRoaming%5CTypora%5Ctypora-user-images%5Cimage-20191202005004514.png" alt="image-20191202005004514"></p><p><img src="C:%5CUsers%5Cpc%5CAppData%5CRoaming%5CTypora%5Ctypora-user-images%5Cimage-20191202005017549.png" alt="image-20191202005017549"></p></li><li><p>修改根目录的_config.yml文件</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">theme: next</span></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>接下来修改具体样式：/themes/next/_config.yml（只提示位置，具体还是看文档比较好）</p></li></ul><h3 id="样式"><a href="#样式" class="headerlink" title="样式"></a>样式</h3><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">scheme:Pisces</span></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="favicon"><a href="#favicon" class="headerlink" title="favicon"></a>favicon</h3><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">favicon:</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">2</span></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">small: &#x2F;images&#x2F;favicon-16x16.png</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">3</span></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">medium: &#x2F;images&#x2F;favicon-32x32.png</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">4</span></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">apple-touch-icon: &#x2F;images&#x2F;...</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">5</span></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">safari-pinned-tab: &#x2F;images&#x2F;...</span></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>推荐<a href="https://realfavicongenerator.net" target="_blank" rel="noopener">一个网站</a>，可以直接将图片转化为站点小图标</p><h3 id="avatar"><a href="#avatar" class="headerlink" title="avatar"></a>avatar</h3><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"># Sidebar Avatar</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">2</span></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">avatar:</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">3</span></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">#...</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">4</span></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">#...</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">5</span></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">#...</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">6</span></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">url: &#x2F;images&#x2F;avatar.png</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">7</span></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">#...</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">8</span></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">rouded: true(是否显示圆形)</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">9</span></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">#...</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">10</span></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">rotated: true(是否旋转)</span></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="RSS"><a href="#RSS" class="headerlink" title="RSS"></a>RSS</h3><p>博客一般需要RSS订阅，如果要开启，需要安装插件：hexo-generator-feed。之后，站点会自动生成RSS Feed文件：</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install hexo-generator-feed --save</span></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>在根目录运行该命令。</p><p>不需要配置，以后编译生成站点会自动生成RSS Feed文件了。</p><h3 id="code"><a href="#code" class="headerlink" title="code"></a>code</h3><p>修改codeblock区域</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">codeblock:</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">2</span></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">#...</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">3</span></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">highlight_theme: night bright</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">4</span></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">#...</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">5</span></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">copy_button:</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">6</span></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">enable: true</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">7</span></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">#...</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">8</span></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">show_result: true</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">9</span></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">#...</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">10</span></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">style: mac</span></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="top"><a href="#top" class="headerlink" title="top"></a>top</h3><p>辅助回到顶部的按钮。</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">back2top:</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">2</span></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">enable: true</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">3</span></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">#...</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">4</span></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sidebar: false为true按钮会出现在侧栏下方</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">5</span></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">#...</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">6</span></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">scrollpercent: true显示阅读百分比</span></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="reading-process"><a href="#reading-process" class="headerlink" title="reading_process"></a>reading_process</h3><p>阅读进度</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">reading_progress:</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">2</span></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">enable: true</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">3</span></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">#...</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">4</span></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">position: top</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">5</span></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">color: &quot;#222&quot;</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">6</span></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">height: 2px</span></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="bookmark"><a href="#bookmark" class="headerlink" title="bookmark"></a>bookmark</h3><p>书签，可以根据阅读历史，在下次打开页面时迅速定位到上次的位置。</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">bookmark:</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">2</span></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">enable: false</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">3</span></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">#...</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">4</span></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">color: &quot;#222&quot;</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">5</span></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">#...</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">6</span></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">save: auto</span></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="github-banner"><a href="#github-banner" class="headerlink" title="github_banner"></a>github_banner</h3><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">github_banner:</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">2</span></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">enable: true</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">3</span></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">permalink: https:&#x2F;&#x2F;github.com&#x2F;ChenyuanYuyang&#x2F;chenyuanyuyang.github.io</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">4</span></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">title: ChenyuanYuyang GitHub</span></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="gitalk"><a href="#gitalk" class="headerlink" title="gitalk"></a>gitalk</h3><p>由于Hexo是静态博客，而且没有连接数据库的功能，所以它的评论功能不可自行集成。但可以集成第三方的服务。</p><p>Next主题提供了多种评论插件的集成：changyan | disqus | disqusjs | facebook_comments_plugin | gitalk | livere | valine | vkontakte</p><p><strong>这里选择以gitalk为例</strong> ，它是利用GitHub的issue当评论的。</p><ul><li><p>首先需要在GitHub注册一个<a href="https://github.com/settings/applications/new" target="_blank" rel="noopener">OAuth Application</a>。注册完拿到Client ID 和 Client Secret就行了。</p></li><li><p>在comments区域配置使用gitalk</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">comments:</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">2</span></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">#...</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">3</span></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">style: tabs</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">4</span></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">#...</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">5</span></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">active: gitalk</span></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>然后找到gitalk配置，添加它的各项配置：</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">gitalk:</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">2</span></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">enable: true</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">3</span></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">github_id: ChenyuanYuyang</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">4</span></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">repo: chenyuanyuyang.github.io #repository name to store issues</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">5</span></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">client_id:</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">6</span></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">client_secret:</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">7</span></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">#GitHub repo owner and collaborators, only these guys can initialize github issues.</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">8</span></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">admin_user: germey </span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">9</span></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">distraction_free_mode : true #Facebook-like distraction feed</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">10</span></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">langauge:zh-CN</span></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>然后就可以使用了，这里设置的评论功能需要用户获取GitHub授权</p></li></ul><h3 id="pangu"><a href="#pangu" class="headerlink" title="pangu"></a>pangu</h3><p>我也有这个强迫症！中英文书写时中间要留有空格。利用pangu可以解决这个麻烦。</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">pangu: true</span></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="math"><a href="#math" class="headerlink" title="math"></a>math</h3><p>有时候会需要公式，比如演示一些算法推导过程</p><p>Next主题提供了两个 <strong>渲染引擎</strong> 分别是 mathjax 和 katex。后者相对前者来说速度更快，而且不需要JS额外支持。但后者支持的功能不如前者丰富。<a href="https://theme-next.org/docs/third-party-services/math-equations" target="_blank" rel="noopener">详情参看</a></p><p>以mathjax为例子</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">math:</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">2</span></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">enable: true</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">3</span></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">...</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">4</span></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">per_page: true</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">5</span></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">...</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">6</span></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">mathjax:</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">7</span></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">enable: true</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">8</span></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">mhchem: true</span></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li><p>mathjax需要额外安装插件，叫做hexo-rendered-kramed，也可安装hexo-renderer-pandoc</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm un hexo-renderer-marked --save</span></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm i hexo-renderer-kramed --save</span></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ul><h3 id="pjax"><a href="#pjax" class="headerlink" title="pjax"></a>pjax</h3><p>pjax技术实际是利用Ajax实现了局部页面的刷新。既可以实现URL的更快，又可以做到无刷新加载。</p><ul><li><p>首先开启pjax功能</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">pjax: true</span></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>安装对应的pjax依赖库</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">cd themes&#x2F;next</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">2</span></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git clone https:&#x2F;&#x2F;github.com&#x2F;theme-next&#x2F;theme-next-pjax source&#x2F;lib&#x2F;pjax</span></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ul><p>更多参看<a href="https://theme-next.org/docs" target="_blank" rel="noopener">官方文档</a></p><h1 id="文章"><a href="#文章" class="headerlink" title="文章"></a>文章</h1><ul><li><p>新建文章：</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo new &#123;fileName&#125;</span></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>文章就会出现在source/_posts文件夹下，是MarkDown格式的。</p></li></ul><p>文章的参数设置参看<a href="https://hexo.io/zh-cn/docs/writing.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">官方文档</a></p><h1 id="标签页"><a href="#标签页" class="headerlink" title="标签页"></a>标签页</h1><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo new page tage</span></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h1 id="分类页"><a href="#分类页" class="headerlink" title="分类页"></a>分类页</h1><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo new page categories</span></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h1 id="搜索页"><a href="#搜索页" class="headerlink" title="搜索页"></a>搜索页</h1><ul><li><p>安装插件：hexo-generator-searchdb</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install hexo-generator-searchdb --save</span></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>在根目录的_config.yml添加搜索设置：</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">search:</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">2</span></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">path: search.xml</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">3</span></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">field: post</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">4</span></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">format: html</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">5</span></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">limit: 10000</span></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>在主题目录的_config.yml修改local_search：</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">local_search:</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">2</span></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">enable: true</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">3</span></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">...</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">4</span></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">trigger: auto</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">5</span></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">top_n_per_article: 5</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">6</span></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">unescape: false</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">7</span></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">preload: false</span></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ul><p>更多请参考<a href="https://theme-next.org/docs/third-party-services/search-services" target="_blank" rel="noopener">这里</a></p><h1 id="404页面"><a href="#404页面" class="headerlink" title="404页面"></a>404页面</h1><ul><li>直接在根目录的source文件夹下新建一个404.md</li><li>书写就看自己了</li></ul><hr><hr><p>官方文档有更多配置，请自行查看：<a href="https://hexo.io/zh-cn/docs/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://hexo.io/zh-cn/docs/</a></p><h1 id="部署脚本"><a href="#部署脚本" class="headerlink" title="部署脚本"></a>部署脚本</h1><p>windows下编写.bat文件。输入</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo clean</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">2</span></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo generate</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">3</span></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo deploy</span></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>与我而言，暂时用不着。</p><h1 id="自定义域名"><a href="#自定义域名" class="headerlink" title="自定义域名"></a>自定义域名</h1><p>在GitHub的Repository的settings下找到GitHub Pages。具体修改，从中看。</p><hr><p>这里打一个 “小吴” 的个人博客网站 <a href="http://www.cxyxiaowu.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">www.cxyxiaowu.com</a> </p><p>因为我是看他写的微信文章搭建的这个博客，感谢他。</p>]]></content>
    
